subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which king introduced the concept of Maharaja in Rajasthan?
question_hi: राजस्थान में महाराजा की कलानिविकिपीडित है। किस राजधानी को किया?
explanation_en: Maharaja Man Singh I is the king who introduced the concept of Maharaja in Rajasthan. Krishnadeva Ray was a minister during the reign of Rana Kumbha and not a ruler.
